    {
        "content": "<p>I had stored it very safely in a pushed branch of some repository somewhere, but I can't for the life of me find it, so it should technically be public but I have no idea where. For me, I just calculated the second derivative, with a bunch of squeeze theorem calculations to handle the removable discontinuity at 1. I did indeed fully formalise Theorem 1 from the paper you linked. <br>\n(I keep looking for this file every month or so, and I always get sad that it's lost <span aria-label=\"sad\" class=\"emoji emoji-2639\" role=\"img\" title=\"sad\">:sad:</span>  )</p>",
